>13. My Sin Bearer. Isa. 53:4, 5, 7, 8, </div><div class="t m2fd xa8 h2d y1c89 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10; Rom. 3:24, 25. </div><div class="t m5d4 x99 h71 y11b3 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE LESSON </div><div class="t m135d x4a h71 yeb0 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sacred Day; Holy Priesthood; </div><div class="t m146a x65 h71 y1521 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sins of the Year </div><div class="t m1856 x71 h6 y114d ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m39c x61 h2d y1466 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Of all the ceremonial sabbaths, </div><div class="t m187c x92 h2d y1ce9 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which was the most solemn? Lev. </div><div class="t m1065 x15 h2d y1c70 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">23:27-32. </div><div class="t m1154 x16 h2d y1347 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NoTE.-&quot;Once a year, on the great Day </div><div class="t m3f0 x15 h2d y1559 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Atonement, the priest entered the most  </div><div class="t m678 x6e h2d y14dc ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">holy place for the cleansing of the sanctu-</div><div class="t m1d7 x6e h2d y1462 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ary. The work there performed completed </div><div class="t m6f3 xbc h2d y11b9 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the yearly round of ministration.&quot;-The </div><div class="t m13b4 xbc h4a y1fda ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Great Controversy, </div><div class="t m1b67 xaa h2d y11e8 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 419. </div><div class="t m12f6 x4b h2d y1bd7 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. Which priest performed the </div><div class="t me1f xbc h2d y11c0 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ceremonies on this day? Ex. 30:10; </div><div class="t m3f4 xbc h2d y1467 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Heb. 9:7. </div><div class="t m2a7d x86 h2b yeec ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.</div><div class="t m446c xac h2d y1127 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m152 x76 h2b y1127 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The </div><div class="t m9f4 x4d h2d y1127 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">work </div><div class="t m130d xd2 h6 y18e9 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0